街敗類賣國賊啦, 好撚明顯佢睇過國家機密之後已經唔撚會咁做"},{"pid":"04e976f2cf0dd6960950fe133a377b7ff8d9c386","tid":1795344,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:24:41.000Z","msg":"14年同19年2次都係美國總統以唔同既方式救撚左你地<br />\n唔撚係濕鳩中國領導人救撚左你地呀<br />\n連邊個救撚左你地都未撚知,就做KOL<br />\n將恩人當係仇人, 將仇人當係恩人<br />\n咁你話,唔撚係害死香港同全世界係咩呀仆街?"},{"pid":"a9b4c329573d7edf4611cef2e93bd6c62df74b5e","tid":1795344,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8c1b5b279bd278ed7f46c3cd45ddb481a645d1f","tid":1795344,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:11:58.000Z","msg":"收皮啦死熱狗又屌泛民搞分化"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:27:32.000Z","msg":"嗱<br />\n樓主今次又講得啱wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0df07205351ec9e626a5959bcbcebefe64e80b7","tid":1795344,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:32:33.000Z","msg":"目前就咁睇國際形勢既話<br />\n你地最愛既超級左膠默克爾先係超級賣國賊呀<br />\n因為佢知道中共偷情報技術都允許華為入德國市場呀<br />\n係痴撚線到當ISIS, 殺人政權都係自己人既痴線左膠呀"},{"pid":"8ff6e06a11c61c4422076a6957a66375580aa97a","tid":1795344,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0df07205351ec9e626a5959bcbcebefe64e80b7","tid":1795344,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:32:33.000Z","msg":"目前就咁睇國際形勢既話<br />\n你地最愛既超級左膠默克爾先係超級賣國賊呀<br />\n因為佢知道中共偷情報技術都允許華為入德國市場呀<br />\n係痴撚線到當ISIS, 殺人政權都係自己人既痴線左膠呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:50:05.000Z","msg":"天下左膠一個樣"},{"pid":"95071fd29a37ccbc566dd2603bcdb433c296ebe3","tid":1795344,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9b4c329573d7edf4611cef2e93bd6c62df74b5e","tid":1795344,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8c1b5b279bd278ed7f46c3cd45ddb481a645d1f","tid":1795344,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-